    "attributes": {
        "action": "Hold a referendum on establishing a federal system of devolution and government",
        "additional_details": "This way the laws and regulations for each part of the country will be set by their own government. A new UK Government, to make decisions about matters that require a UK approach, should be established with each of the national governments as a member.",
        "background": "The Government should hold a referendum on granting full autonomy for Wales, Scotland, Northern Ireland and England, with an English Parliament being created. This should help to diffuse tensions in the union.",
